thread.title_full: BRIEF-Dalet H1 operating loss narrows to 2.7 mln euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Dalet H1 operating loss narrows to 2.7 mln euros
text:
Sept 14 Dalet SA :
* Reported on Sunday an H1 operating loss of 2.7 million euros ($3.1 million) versus a loss of 2.9 million euros year ago
* H1 net loss attributable to the group 3.3 million euros versus loss of 3.2 million euros year ago
